<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Database Reset Complete - Ethiopian Vote System</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/reset_success.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="success-container">
      <div class="success-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
      </div>
      <h2 class="success-title">Database Reset Complete</h2>

      <div class="reset-details">
        <strong>The following has been reset:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>All voter data has been cleared</li>
          <li>All votes have been removed</li>
          <li>All parties restored to default set</li>
          <li>All admin users removed (except original super admin)</li>
          <li>All audit logs and activity logs cleared</li>
          <li>System settings restored to defaults</li>
          <li>All sequences reset to initial values</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p class="success-message">
        The Ethiopian Voting System has been successfully reset to its initial state.
        The original super admin account remains intact for system management.
      </p>

      <a href="/admin/login" class="back-btn">
        <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>
        Return to Admin Login
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
